

I am building an app, compatible with API 34 for use in Android 14.0, using Kotlin, Room Library, MSAL for OneDrive integration, Jetpack compose, and KSP plugin.

The app is called RoutineTurboA. It's functionality is like a to-do app, but it covers the entire 24 hours in a day. It starts from 00:01 and ends on 23:59. Each task starts from the previous task's end time.

 I am beginner and I built most of this using help from AI tools, including yourself. So the code may not be perfect or standard. I need your help in building and refining this app. I am interesting in learning as well as building this application. And the most important thing:  Use latest knowledge when helping me - latest API, methods, approach, should be latest, as applicable in year 2024. Do not help me with anything that's deprecated or no longer valid.

